title: New: araabMUZIK – Never Have to Worry
body:
With the crazy amount of high-profile production credits floating **araabMUZIK**’s way recently it’s nice to see him drop some new solo productions.

This new cut, _never have to worry_, taken from his upcoming _For Professional Use Only_ mixtape has club banger written all over it. Never change **araabMUZIK**.

_For Professional Use Only_ _is released on the 15th of Feb._
